people are wearing them?

00:41:05.800 --> 00:41:07.780
DIANE VON FURSTENBERG:
I met those girls.

00:41:07.780 --> 00:41:10.360
I think I was the first
person that they came to see

00:41:10.360 --> 00:41:12.060
